The paper deals with coordination of networked systems, which is a topic studied in the field of control systems (cs.SY) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA). The use of hybrid dynamical systems also suggests cs.DC as a possible sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of communication policies and limited precision in communication, which are relevant to networked systems and machine learning (cs.NE). Finally, the paper mentions a self-triggered "gossip" coordination system, which falls under the category of distributed computing (cs.LG).
